    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313170/extras/c84846b9ab623d0b61dce40858110214.avif?t=1731320667\" width=600 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Wishlist for support !</strong></h2><br>Genre : Action, Platformer, Fighting, Rumble battle<br><br><strong>Clash of Digital : Rumble Smash</strong> is platformer rumble battle game. Franchise game from <strong>`Clash of Digital`</strong> title. A digital clashing rumble battle between character based on their skill and techniques to see who is the strongest. There are various kinds of playable characters, each one has their own skill and techniques. Different items with various kind of power that can be helpful for player. Complete an adventure to unlock each new characters and maps.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key features : </strong></h2>* Unlockable character and map<br>* 4 local multiplayer battle<br>* Adventure mode : Unlock new character and map stage by completing a quest<br>* Free battle program : Free play battle with your friends or COM<br>* Steam remote play together : Play with your friends using Steam remote play feature<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game mode : </strong></h2>* Normal mode : Normal battle mode with life data count<br>* Virus mode :  Protect yourself from virus and infect back while infected<br>* Catch &amp; run mode : Catch while you not have stick &amp; run while you have stick. Longest player who have the stick is winner<br>* Time mode : Beat opponent as much as possible while the timer is running, highest life data count is winner<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Character unlockable system : </strong></h2>Complete an adventure to unlock new character !<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313170/extras/1df6fae6f876bca7442d47704090c376.avif?t=1731320667\" width=600 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Map unlockable system : </strong></h2>Complete an adventure to unlock new map stage !<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313170/extras/f18cdb01040b5f14ea68569435ce3dbe.avif?t=1731320667\" width=600 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Full guide combo &amp; controller system : </strong></h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313170/extras/66976e1c684c1e4f794740eba6d53eec.avif?t=1731320667\" width=600 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Demo content : </strong></h2>- Play as Ryu only on adventure<br><br>- 4 local multiplayer battle with 4 character only and game mode customization. There are 4 playable characters and 3 map stages.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313170/extras/ecb9d0e5bbd9dd8833f204446d7303f7.avif?t=1731320667\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313170/extras/8456e65907ff584bf3fecbdfb37d8dea.avif?t=1731320667\" width=150 height=150 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313170/extras/cfdeaf4c8e593957dca9741c3a986891.avif?t=1731320667\" width=150 height=150 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313170/extras/dffced129621cf368009dee8c8d0e26f.avif?t=1731320667\" width=150 height=150 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2313170/extras/6e3593fa39fc341efb29cf7fc7bd5c74.avif?t=1731320667\" width=150 